# id: HandlerMethodArgumentResolver -> Object resolveArgument(MethodParameter parameter, Message<?> message) throws Exception_
commentText: Resolves a method parameter into an argument value from a given message._@param parameter the method parameter to resolve. This parameter must_have previously been passed to_{@link #supportsParameter(org.springframework.core.MethodParameter)}_and it must have returned {@code true}_@param message the currently processed message_@return the resolved argument value, or {@code null}._@throws Exception in case of errors with the preparation of argument values
